This JSON outlines a complete n8n workflow for an AI Agent triggered by a webhook. It includes the Agent node, connected to an OpenAI Chat Model (placeholder GPT-4.1), Simple Memory, and several tools (Gmail, Airtable, HTTP Request), finally responding to the initial webhook:

